    "description": "A CLI that extends ansible, ansible-playbook, and ansible-vault to use the system keyring for vault passwords",
    "github_id": "R_kgDOG5d3jg",
    "gitlab_group_id": "14289563",
    "gitlab_project_id": "33995299",
    "group": "python",
    "name": "Ansible Keyring",
    "overview": "This repository is home to **[ansible-keyring](https://github.com/ProfessorManhattan/ansible-keyring)** a CLI that extends the `ansible`, `ansible-playbook`, and `ansible-vault` command to retrieve vault passwords from the system keyring. It is based on the work of [ansible-tools](https://pypi.org/project/ansible-tools/) with a couple usability improvements. The features it adds are:\n\n* Does not have to be run only in directories where `ansible.cfg` is present\n* New, shorter, more intuitive command aliases",
    "repository": {
      "github": "https://github.com/ProfessorManhattan/ansible-keyring",
      "gitlab": "https://gitlab.com/megabyte-labs/python/cli/ansible-keyring"
    },
    "slug": "ansible-keyring",
    "subgroup": "cli",
    "title": "Ansible Keyring - A System Keyring Integration CLI"
  },
  "changelog": {
    "displayTypes": [
      "feat",
      "fix",
      "perf",
      "refactor",
      "revert"
